	(text "Maximum power-up time delay for Flash instruction readiness is 10ms.\nAccording to the DS181 AMD datasheet, the minimum FPGA Power-On Reset\nTPOR is also 10ms. By implementing a capacitor on the PROGRAM_B pin of\nthe FPGA, the startup sequence is intentionally delayed to ensure a safe\nmargin where the Flash initializes prior to the FPGA."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 338.074 141.986 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "3366b632-5067-4603-b391-958139377338")
	)
